officials; rabbis and synagogues; and Soviet Jewry. Includes also material on the public conferences of the Council; Council publications and releases; and photographs of Council activities and individuals connected with the <b>Council.</b> <b>Jewish</b> Community <b>Council</b> of Metropolitan Boston established 1944. far 031...|$|R
